            <li><strong>Borehole Diameter:</strong> 6–10 inch</li>
            <li><strong>Soil Types:</strong> Clay, rock, hard formations</li>
            <li><strong>Drilling Speed:</strong> 25–40 feet/hour (variable)</li>
